import React from 'react' import "../styles/tour-details.css" import { Col, Container, Row, Form, ListGroup } from 'reactstrap'; import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; import tourData from "../assets/data/tours" const TourDetails = () => { const { id } = useParams() const tour = tourData.find(tour => tour.id === id) const { photo, title, desc, price, reviews, city, distance, maxGroupSize } = tour return <>

{title}
} export default TourDetails
